; Coverage test for xact.cc
; Tests verify() skipping postings that don't must_balance().
; Unbalanced virtual postings ((Account)) have must_balance() = false,
; so verify() skips them when checking the transaction balance.

2024/03/01 Test with virtual
    Expenses:Food     $10.00
    Assets:Cash      $-10.00
    (Memo:Notes)       $5.00

test reg
24-Mar-01 Test with virtual     Expenses:Food                $10.00       $10.00
                                Assets:Cash                 $-10.00            0
                                (Memo:Notes)                  $5.00        $5.00
end test

test bal
             $-10.00  Assets:Cash
              $10.00  Expenses:Food
               $5.00  Memo:Notes
--------------------
               $5.00
end test
